      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>That \"keep fighting\" thing is the problem though. It feels like I'm just fighting a war that's already been lost. Every day is just a new version of the same hell. Sometimes I think the only real \"relief\" would be if everything just... went quiet. Like, permanently. Does that sound crazy?",
